snippet.title: Flufftopia Trailer | Version 1.1 - Indie Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Download at Itch.io: https://smokesomefrogs.itch.io/flufftopia

Website: http://smokesomefrogs.com/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/smokesomefrogs

Flufftopia is a cute little idle game with a story. You help to grow a Flufftown into a Flufftopia! But maybe … there is something more?
